  "content": "\n \n \n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075857\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"386\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e34e0f4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIG4Fr65p0RnqSBIOq6TOJbSPUFy83scv9TIPeRibdnZwcZelwu2lvrTtEWNCbZ4l7jTUuwdKerZRoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;overscroll-behavior: contain;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Rototo, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 1px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">7月24日消息，经过长达12个月的追踪，并基于海量的ChatGPT用户数据，OpenAI首席经济学家罗尼·查特吉（Ronnie Chatterji）领导的团队近日发布了名为《解锁经济机会》（Unlocking Economic Opportunity）的深度报告，揭示了AI对经济增长的巨大潜力。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075858\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6197916666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"358\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=70319746&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIG4Fr65p0RnqSBIOq6TOJbSrZTxAicKZ0AcEc89SCBVZsMqNy4zXicz93f5uefibUhsms1svnVJDSGgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544058943\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1270815074496056\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1141\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09e5945c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIFNmictFHYdncDXcq2icHxwTK56dgibfgrWYob2quE8oGtLxx75S8uw6wlJmuVUo870E4Ya3DraUcZaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0pt 0pt 24px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(23, 91, 190);\">史上增长最快的消费级应用</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">报告表示，ChatGPT的崛起速度，堪称科技史上的奇迹。</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它仅用5天就达到了100万用户，2个月内突破1亿用户大关，而如今，其全球用户数量已超过5亿</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075861\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3193069306930693\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"808\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"185\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6d37b606&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIG4Fr65p0RnqSBIOq6TOJbSET5CCibByp2LibuOa8Jnl17TibnZV90bVevtDSj7weFym63Rthxicmtz7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种前所未有的用户增长，直接反映了其在工作场景中的广泛渗透。数据显示，</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">美国职场成年人中，工作中使用ChatGPT的人数已从2023年的8%飙升至28%</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">每天，</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">全球用户向ChatGPT发送的消息超过25亿条，仅美国用户每天就贡献了3.3亿条</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。这种爆炸性的互动量为OpenAI提供了一个独特的视角，使其能够深入观察AI对经济产生的真实影响。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，在美国，ChatGPT的主要使用场景包括支持学习和提升书面沟通能力，分别占所有美国消息（指来自美国用户在ChatGPT上的所有对话内容消息）的20%和18%。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结合其广泛的应用场景、持续飙升的采用率以及免费使用的特点，使得ChatGPT本身不仅仅是一个工具，更是提升个人生产力的关键驱动力，并成为衡量AI对宏观经济影响的重要指标。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI的报告深入剖析了ChatGPT采用率激增的背后动因，并结合来自美国的ChatGPT对话数据，以及经济学研究、外部调查和预测，评估AI对美国经济增长的潜在贡献。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">即便是像电力和蒸汽机这样的通用技术，也需要几十年的时间才被广泛采用，并产生显著的经济效益。而</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT仅仅发布两个月，月活跃用户就已突破1亿大关。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">仅仅两年，ChatGPT的普及速度就达到了互联网的两倍！ 截至2024年，半数美国成年人已经亲身体验过AI产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544058942\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1270815074496056\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data