top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">客户获取与支持：AI工具让企业触达并支持客户变得前所未有的轻松。呼叫中心员工使用OpenAI模型后，回应客户咨询的生产力平均提高了14%。</span></span></strong></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">咨询行业：咨询师们使用OpenAI的GPT-4，工作效率提升了25%，任务数量增加了12%，而工作质量提高了40%。</span></span></strong></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-top